No. 11-6085. Mindy Zied-Campbell, Petitioner v. Estelle Richman, Secretary, Pennsylvania Department of Public Welfare, et al. 565 U.S. 961, 132 S. Ct. 464,

181 L. Ed. 2d 291,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 7478. October 17, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pauperis denied, and petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 428 Fed. Appx. 224.
